KeysToEntries.story_1_3_000:
Figures… Kazumi’s gone
and this is who
shows up.
KeysToEntries.story_1_3_001_1:
Whoever’s fastest in the
hills is the real king.
KeysToEntries.story_1_3_002_1: And that’s why it’s a shame.
KeysToEntries.story_1_3_002_2:
Tonight’s weak excuse
for a battle.
KeysToEntries.story_1_3_003_1:
Let’s start over!
If it’s not full throttle,
it means nothing!
KeysToEntries.story_1_3_004:
It never made the records…
the night before the legend.
KeysToEntries.story_1_3_005:
On the quiet shores of Lake Akina…
the legend begins.
